<h2>Viewport Visibility</h2>
<p>These classes give you the option to show or hide elements in certain viewports xs, sm, md, lg, xl</p>
<p>Where size is one of:</p>
<ul>
  <li>xs - targets from 0 to 575px</li>
  <li>sm - targets from 576px to 767px</li>
  <li>md - targets from 768px to 991px</li>
  <li>lg - targets from 992px to 1199px</li>
  <li>xl - targets from 1200px upwards</li>
</ul>
<p>Where display is one of:</p>
<ul>
  <li>show - displays the elements</li>
  <li>hide - hides the elements</li>
</ul>
<p>The classes are named using the format nsw-{display}-{size}</p>
